	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">De Mirandula interrogavi d. <persName type="auto_name">Cęlium</persName>, qui dixit a mercatoribus accepisse,</foreign> das die Barfuͤsser mönch haben ein capitel zuͦ Mirandula instituiert; vil münch sindt kommen, haben harnasch, der merer theil pantzerhembder und buchsen bracht uff den eslen; sindt iren vil worden, die etlich Spanier kriegknecht, sind under inen gsin, haben die stat wellen anderen öffnen by nacht und dem keyserischen kriegsvolck uberantworten.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dessen ist man innen worden, die münch by nacht gfangen, die kriegsmünch gehenckt mit anderen münchen.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed <persName type="auto_name">Celius</persName> expectat literas et fortassis a domino <persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerio</persName> brevi audies certiorem historiam hac de re.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic omnia videmus agi proditionibus et dolis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi etiam in primis literis de episcopis<note type="misc">darüber v. Bullingers Hand: "Mogunt[ino</note>, Trevir[ensi] et Colonien[si].] ad Confluentiam congregatis, idque est verum; adiunxit se Palatinus Rheni, et alii episcopi<note type="misc">"Herbipolen[sis</note> etc."] miserunt legatos ad illum conventum.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quibus de rebus putas illos consultaturos?<note type="misc">"De Magdeburgen[sibus</note> pacandis, de Ferd[inando] et Philippo pacandis."]</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Caesar</persName> plaga domini aggravatus est, ut nesciat, quo se vertat, etsi dominum illum persequi non cessat nec illi gloriam propriam dare vult in istis plagis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praeterea rogavit tabellarius, ut tibi significem se literas probe curasse, etsi mihi non dederit; incidit enim forte fortuna in illum, cui inscriptę erant.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neque hoc te latere volo, etsi ridiculum sit, in nostro macello hodie nullus bos nec vacca mactata sunt; servabimus in crastinum ieiunium quadragesimale ascensuri in cęlum, ubi hiis carnalibus rebus opus non habemus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileę</placeName> 6. maii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus <persName type="auto_name">Naogeorgos</persName> te salutat officiosissime.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis nomine meo d. <persName type="auto_name">Theodorum</persName>, optimum virum, qui absque dubio tristitia non dicenda afficitur ob <persName type="auto_name">Eleazari</persName><note type="misc">darüber von Bullingers Hand: "<persName type="auto_name">Köllin</persName>"</note> mortem subitaneam.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale aeternum.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A domino <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconio</persName> literas accipies absque dubio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName ref="p1278" cert="high">Gastius</persName> ex animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem wolgelerten herren meyster Heinrych Bullinger, lütpriester zuͦ Zurich, mynem gunstigen, lieben herren, zuͦ handen.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zürich.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
